evidence.claim: FactorCloud utilizes AWS services including Lambda and API Gateway for their platform infrastructure.
The platform is designed with HIPAA compliance, ensuring secure handling of health information.
FactorCloud implements HL7 standards for health data integration and sharing.
They offer RESTful API integration capabilities to enhance system interoperability.
